njandukalude nattil oridavela ( english : an intermission in the land of crabs ) is an upcoming indian malayalam comedy film directed and co-written by althaf salim . it stars nivin pauly , ahaana krishna and aishwarya lekshmi in lead roles , along with lal , shanthi krishna , siju wilson , sharafudheen , and krishnashankar . it is produced by nivin pauly himself under his home production banner , pauly jr . pictures .